theorem closure_interior_union_eq_closure_interiors {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    {A B : Set X} :
    closure (interior (A ∪ B)) = closure (interior A ∪ interior B) := by
  simpa [interior_union]

theorem closure_interior_union_eq {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A B : Set X} :
    closure (interior (A ∪ B)) = closure (interior A) ∪ closure (interior B) := by
  simpa [interior_union, closure_union]

theorem closure_interior_subset_closure {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    closure (interior A) ⊆ closure A := by
  exact closure_mono (interior_subset : interior A ⊆ A)
